			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//entertainment.slashdot.org/story/25/02/22/0638211/james-bonds-next-assignment-amazon-pays-1-billion-for-full-creative-control#comments" title="">34</a></span>
		
	</h1>
	<div class="details" id="details-176339913">
